OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy with a few spots
OL,6,Fof light rain, but mainly dry with
OL,7,Fsome bright spells around the Moray
OL,8,FFirth.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA rather cloudy evening with
OL,11,Fa few showery outbreaks of rain
OL,12,Fspreading north. Rain will turn
OL,13,Foccasionally heavy for a time across
OL,14,FCaithness and Sutherland before
OL,15,Fturning generally drier later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA rather cloudy start to
OL,18,Fthe morning with patchy light rain.
OL,19,FTurning brighter through the day with
OL,20,Fsunny spells and scattered showers,
OL,21,Fone or two on the heavier side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
